transcript:
Customer: Haan sir.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello, haan ji sir.
Customer: Haan sir, good morning.
Executive: Namaskar sir ji.
Customer: Haan haan bas bas karwa raha hu sir.
Customer: Do char minute ruk jaiye bas karwa raha hu.
Executive: Bhej rahe ho link ji?
Customer: Haan haan link aise mail pe gaya hua hai aapko.
Executive: Mail pe gaya hua hai, dekha nahi.
Customer: Haan mail pe aaya hua hai.

Customer: Gaya nahi ji?
Customer: Ek minute ji ek minute.

Customer: Receive aaya hua hai link.
Customer: Video meet hai.
Customer: Bole do usko.

Customer: Ho rahe ho park chalo.
Customer: Double ji double ha padta hai thoda naam likha.
Customer: Kispe karna hai seedha?

Customer: Mere to lagdi pala karwa di.


Customer: Padta hai to dekhte mail pe aaya hua.

Customer: Thode se upar bas khojna tha. Ab dekh email ha.

Customer: Wo password nahi hai duja 100 wala kar lena.
Customer: Jidharo wifi karna padta.

Customer: Haan haan parso hi chala gaya tha. Kal hnera parso hi chala gaya tha.

Customer: Full te kar loge na.
Customer: Fir mai to aap se yahi gal karta hu, wo koi bande funde je le leni hai bas. Ha. Wo bhi aa.
Customer: Aage se koi set karaya hua hai inna to.


Customer: To kam kara aaj.
summary:

- Customer having trouble finding the meeting link.

- Executive confirmed link sent to customer's email.
